# Ship after every change

When you finish a requested change in this repo:

1. Run the narrowest useful check (`npm run check` or a narrower command).
2. Commit with a clear message.
3. Push to `main`.
4. Deploy when the Worker, build output, or served assets changed (`npm run deploy`).
5. Verify on the live site at `https://los.tre.systems` — not just `tsc` or `curl /healthz` alone; open the affected pages in a browser and confirm behavior.

Do not leave completed work uncommitted or undeployed unless the user explicitly says not to.
